		The Merchants of Norrath exist to encourage roleplaying through traveling 
		the lands and selling our wares.  We intend to bring fair prices and 
		honorable trading to all continents.  A customer knows that when they 
		purchase from one of our Merchants they will receive a fair trade and if 
		they are not happy we will do what it takes to please them.
		<P>
		As a guild, our secondary goal is to provide a means for personal advancement 
		for our members.  By pooling our talents and strengths we expand our 
		possibilities well beyond what we could hope to achieve as individuals. The
		guild acts as a network that covers every corner of Norrath.  Our members can 
		be sure to get assistance no matter where their travels may take them.
